<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Roadster Revival - Car Parts Repair Facility</title>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.4/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Reset and Box Sizing */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Body Styling */
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* Main Container */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            padding: 40px;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* Heading Styles */
        h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #e74c3c;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-weight: 300;
        }

        /* Content Section */
        .content-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        /* Text Content Styling */
        .content-text {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #ccc;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        /* Button Styling */
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 25px;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #c0392b;
        }

        /* Car Parts Image Section */
        .car-images {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .car-images img {
            width: 300px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .car-images img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        /* Media Queries for Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 40px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }

            .content-text {
                font-size: 16px;
            }

            .btn {
                font-size: 18px;
                padding: 12px 24px;
            }

            .car-images img {
                width: 250px;
                height: 160px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }

            .content-text {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .btn {
                font-size: 16px;
                padding: 10px 20px;
            }

            .car-images {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }

            .car-images img {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 30px;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .content-text {
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .btn {
                font-size: 14px;
                padding: 8px 16px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Heading Section -->
        <h1>Car Parts Repair Facility</h1>
        <h2>Expert Repair Services for Your Classic Car Parts</h2>

        <!-- Content Section -->
        <div class="content-section">
            <!-- Text Section -->
            <div class="content-text">
                <p>
                    At **Roadster Revival**, we pride ourselves on offering premium car parts repair services for vintage and classic cars. Whether your car needs engine components, suspension repairs, or any other mechanical part restored to its original glory, our team of expert technicians ensures that every repair is done with the utmost care and precision.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We understand that keeping your classic car in top condition requires more than just maintenance – it requires expertise. That’s why Roadster Revival employs a team of highly skilled mechanics and craftsmen who specialize in the intricate details of vintage car parts. From sourcing hard-to-find components to restoring parts that have seen decades of use, we bring your car back to life, one part at a time.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our repair services cover a wide range of car parts including engines, transmissions, brakes, suspension systems, and electrical components. We also offer custom solutions tailored to your vehicle's needs, ensuring that your car performs like new while maintaining its original charm.
                </p>
                <p>
                    No matter the condition of your classic car parts, we guarantee professional, efficient, and reliable repairs that keep your car running smoothly for years to come.
                </p>
                <a href="repair quote.html" class="btn">Request a Repair Quote</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Car Parts Images Section -->
            <div class="car-images">
                <img src="image/engine_497x360.jpg">
                <img src="image/istockphoto-490267829-612x612.jpg">
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
